embeds.title: Support Hub
embeds.description:
Let us know if you have any questions or concerns! Help is only a few clicks away!
​

fields.name: File a Case
fields.value:
> All SCP Site53 members have the right to file a case. There is no guarantee on how long this may take. Click on the menu below to file a case.
​

fields.name: Getting Started
fields.value: > Check out the secrets and lore behind [SCP Site53](https://sites.google.com/view/scpsite53). You can also view information about our staff, whitelisted department, and other resources.

fields.name: Community Support
fields.value: Review [online forums](https://discord.com/channels/932845698662162432/1060767820050337903) created by our Site53 enthusiasts, experts, and staff members. This is the quickest option.
